Package edu.brown.cs.cdluo.stars

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Dimen
    Holds coordinates that are the basis for positioning in the KDTree.
    DistComparator
    Comparator for distances in DQEntry.
    DistQueue
    A Bounded Priority Queue of DQEntries, where distance is the distance from the testpoint the queue was instantiated with to the star.
    DQEntry
    This class represents an entry in DistanceQueue.
    DumbTree
    A Dumb version of my KDTree.
    KDNode
    Represents a node in the KDTree by keeping track of a star along with a left and right child.
    KDTree
    The KDTree class, which contains most of the logic of the program.
    Main
    Main method, which executes all the functionality of the program.
    Star
    This class represents a star by holding all the information from the csv file.
    StarComparator
    Comparator that sorts stars by a dimension x,y,or z represented by curDimen.
    StarGenDummy
    Generates arrays of stars for testing.
